Package: drma
Title: Dose-Response Meta-Analysis with a meta/netmeta-Style Interface
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Yuuki", "Furukawa", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A user-friendly wrapper around the dosresmeta package for
    dose-response meta-analysis. Accepts arm-level data in long format and
    automatically computes OR, RR, MD, or SMD before fitting restricted cubic
    spline dose-response curves. Provides plot methods with bubble overlays,
    rug marks for tested doses, multi-curve overlay, and a pairwise league
    table for comparing arbitrary dose pairs.
